-- MOVES-EY appoints Guerzoni as EMEIA transaction advisory services leader
-- 
-- Mon Sep 22, 2014 01:39PM EDT
-- None



Sept 22 (Reuters) - Audit firm EY appointed Andrea Guerzoni as its transaction advisory services leader for the Europe, Middle East, India and Africa (EMEIA) region, effective immediately.

Guerzoni, who will be leading a team of more than 6,100, has been with EY for nearly 20 years, working in audit, corporate finance and transaction roles.